            "value": "Create queue is not using the region to correctly create the queue on the specified Amazon Endpoint.\r\nAmazon has four endpoints that can be used based on your location http:\/\/docs.amazonwebservices.com\/AWSSimpleQueueService\/2009-02-01\/SQSDeveloperGuide\/\r\nCreate is not using the region parameter to create queues on the correct endpoint.\r\n\r\nIn Zend_Service_Amazon_Sqs the _makeRequest method should take into account the region that was specified in the constructor.\r\n\r\n$client->setUri('http:\/\/'.$this->_sqsEndpoint); "
